headline.main: AP Interview: Russian Protester Decries Prison Conditions
headline.print_headline: AP Interview: Russian Protester Decries Prison Conditions

lead_paragraph: With the Eiffel Tower as a backdrop, French conservative Francois Fillon clung tenaciously to his presidential candidacy Sunday, urging thousands of supporters at a high-stakes rally not to flee his ship despite escalating pressure to step aside because of impending corruption charges.
